model.name: Archlight Flat Ballerina
model.disambiguatingDescription: The Archlight flat slingback ballerina takes inspiration from the cult LV Archlight sneaker for a design that is both sporty and elegant. Crafted from technical satin and Monogram canvas, it features an adjustable velcro strap at the back and an ultra-flexible rubber outsole. It is finished with the LV Circle logo and the Louis Vuitton signature in rubber.

additionalProperty.name: detailedDescription
additionalProperty.value:
• Black
  • Technical satin and patent Monogram canvas
  • Velcro strap
  • Supple rubber outsole
  • LV Circle signature
  • Louis Vuitton signature on the strap
  • Made in Italy
